THIRD-PARTY CONTENT
-------------------

Some sentence items in this repository are derived from the Tatoeba
Project (https://tatoeba.org), licensed under CC-BY 2.0. Such items
carry a "license" block with "sourceId": "tatoeba-cc-by-2.0" and the
original Tatoeba sentence IDs. The aggregate attribution list is
maintained in `licenses/attribution.json`. Tatoeba terms apply to
those items in addition to CC-BY 4.0 for the surrounding lesson
structure.

CC-BY 2.0 full legal text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/legalcode

